comments: Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Westbrook's (WAS) path.
Harden (BKN) makes marginal contact with Mathews (WAS) as he stops and releases from Mathews at the end of the drive.
Harden (BKN) makes contact with the ball during Len's (WAS) shot attempt. Any arm contact is marginal and occurs after the ball contact.
Harris (BKN) makes incidental contact with Westbrook (WAS) as he falls backwards and the two players pursue the rebound.
Beal (WAS) firms up in Harris' (BKN) path and does not deliver any contact during the screen.
Harris (BKN) legally contests Mathews' (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Hachimura (WAS) makes contact with Irving's (BKN) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Beal (WAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Green's (BKN) path and does not deliver any contact.
Claxton (BKN) does not make any contact with Hachimura (WAS) during his play at the basket.
Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Beal's (WAS) path.
As Harden's (BKN) momentum continues to bring him forward, Len (WAS) makes marginal contact with Harden after the release of his driving shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) makes contact with Mathews' (WAS) lower body that impedes his ability to rebound.
Len (WAS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Green's (BKN) path.
Claxton (BKN) maintains a legal defensive position during Westbrook's (WAS) driving shot attempt.
Harris (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Westbrook's (WAS) path.
Irving (BKN) naturally loses his balance during the drive.
Mathews (WAS) jumps A to B and makes contact with Claxton's (BKN) body during his play at the basket.
Green (BKN) legally contests Westbrook's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
Beal (WAS) makes hand on ball contact and dislodges the ball from Irving (BKN).
Mathews (WAS) grabs Irving's (BKN) arm during his dribble.
